title: Andrea Bocelli Ft. Jane Zhang - Embrace in Love and Dream
description:
Andrea Bocelli Ft. Jane Zhang - Embrace in Love and Dream (Candidate song for 2008 Beijing Summer Olympics Opening Ceremony Song). Includes MP3 songs and AVI music videos.

Music by David Foster
Lyrics by Amy Foster
Released March 12, 2008

MP3: 320 kbps CBR
AVI: XviD

English and Mandarin versions of the song are included with this download, as well as unofficial Music Videos (from YouTube).
